> "\n" [Continue]
> "\"It wasn't,\" I reply. \"But I doubt you'd understand.\"\n" [Continue]
> "He simply nods.\n" [Continue]
> "\"Go on with your confession.\"\n" [Continue]
> "That gives me pause. I hadn't thought of it as such. But I suppose he's right. I am about to admit what I did.\n" [Continue]
